repository-code: "https://github.com/airi-utcn/AMD-ontology"
url: "https://w3id.org/amd-ontology"
abstract: >
  A fully agentic pipeline for constructing and maintaining an OWL ontology
  for Age-Related Macular Degeneration (AMD) from PubMed abstracts.
  Three specialised LangChain agents handle literature discovery, incremental
  knowledge extraction with delta validation, and ontology-wide quality assurance.
  DL-Learner CELOE is used for axiom discovery across 17 learning problems.
  The resulting ontology contains 11 classes, 104 individuals, and 114 triples,
  with 77-81% UMLS alignment.
